Validation Rule Detail
 
Rule Name	Check_blank_fields	Active	Checked

Error Condition Formula
AND(
ISCHANGED(IsConverted),
IsConverted,
(ISBLANK(Email) || ISBLANK(Phone) || ISBLANK( TEXT(LeadSource)))
)

Error Message	- Email, Phone and Lead Source should be populated before Lead conversion.	Error Location	Top of Page
